\c 142
\s Umkhuleko wokucela ukusizwa ekuhluphekeni
\d IMasikili kaDavida, umkhuleko esebhalwini
\p
\v 1 Ngakhalela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni ngelizwi lami\x + Hlab. 77.1.\x*, ngelizwi lami eN\nd kosi\nd*ni ngancenga\x + Hlab. 30.8.\x*.
\v 2 Ngathulula\x + Hlab. 102.\x* isikhalazo sami phambi kwayo, ngatshengisa ukuhlupheka kwami phambi kwayo\x + Jobe 15.4.\x*.
\p
\v 3 Lapho umoya wami uphela amandla phakathi kwami, wena wayazi indlela yami\x + Hlab. 143.4. Hlab. 102. Hlab. 77.3.\x*. Endleleni engihamba ngayo bangifihlele umjibila\x + Hlab. 140.5.\x*.
\v 4 Khangela\x + Is. 63.5. Hlab. 69.20.\x* ngakwesokunene, ubone\x + Hlab. 16.8.\x*, kodwa wayengekho ongaziyo; isiphephelo sangehlula, kakho owakhathalela umphefumulo wami\x + Ruthe 2.10,19.\x*.
\v 5 Ngakhalela kuwe, N\nd kosi\nd*, ngathi\x + Hlab. 140.6.\x*: Wena uyisiphephelo sami\x + Hlab. 14.6.\x*, isabelo sami\x + Hlab. 16.5.\x* elizweni labaphilayo\x + Hlab. 27.13.\x*.
\v 6 Lalela ukukhala kwami\x + Hlab. 17.1.\x*, ngoba ngehliselwe phansi kakhulu\x + Hlab. 79.8. Hlab. 116.6.\x*. Ngikhulula kwabangizingelayo, ngoba balamandla kulami\x + Hlab. 18.17.\x*.
\v 7 Khupha umphefumulo wami entolongweni, ukuze ngidumise ibizo lakho\x + Hlab. 143.11.\x*. Abalungileyo bazangibuthanela, ngoba uzangiphatha kuhle kakhulu\x + Hlab. 13.6.\x*.
